{"word":"ἐπιχράομαι","slug":"ἐπιχράομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπιχράομαι</b></el> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to make use of besides</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a> <a href='S:person, personal'>pers.</a>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>uti, to have dealings with, be friends with</el>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}